aVa journalist was asking him a question about the news feed.
p5
aVAnd the journalist was asking him,
p6
aV"Why is this so important?"
p7
aVAnd Zuckerberg said,
p8
aV"A squirrel dying in your front yard
p9
aVmay be more relevant to your interests right now
p10
aVthan people dying in Africa."
