aa(lp80
VSo it's not just Google and Facebook either.
p81
aVThis is something that's sweeping the Web.
p82
aVThere are a whole host of companies that are doing this kind of personalization.
p83
aVYahoo News, the biggest news site on the Internet,
p84
aVis now personalized \u2014 different people get different things.
p85
aVHuffington Post, the Washington Post, the New York Times \u2014
p86
aVall flirting with personalization in various ways.
p87
aVAnd this moves us very quickly
p88
aVtoward a world in which
p89
aVthe Internet is showing us what it thinks we want to see,
p90
aVbut not necessarily what we need to see.
